My suitcase wouldn't even fit between the bed and the TV, I had to lift it over.	The only recomendation would be to upgrade the TV's and add CNN as one of their channel selections.	The bed was so comfortable, pillows were like from the TV advert.	The breakfast buffet on the rooftop terrace was excellent-it had everything from pancakes and fresh fruit to pastries and meats.	The king size bed in our room (room 115) was the most comfortable of our entire Italy trip.	The management even sent a box of chocolate and a bottle of wine to our room, since my husband has elite status.